'''班加拉姆環礁'''（{{lang-ml|'''ബങ്കാരം'''}}，{{lang-en|'''Bangaram Atoll'''}}）是一個位於[[印度|印度]][[聯邦屬地|聯邦屬地]][[拉克沙群島|拉克沙群島]]中的[[環礁|環礁]]。該環礁長8.1公里、寬4.2公里，距離印度本土城市[[柯枝|柯枝]]約400公里。該環礁距離最近的拉克沙群島島嶼[[阿格蒂島|阿格蒂島]]約7公里。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oceandots.com/indian/lakshadweep/bangaram.php |title=Bangaram - Oceandots |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archive-date=2010-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101223043232/http://www.oceandots.com/indian/lakshadweep/bangaram.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>'''班加拉姆島'''是該環礁中的主要島嶼，島上並沒登記戶口的常駐居民，但島上有座渡假村，該渡假村雇員為61名。<ref name=lakshadweep-11thplan>{{cite web|url=http://lakshadweep.nic.in/FiveYearPlan_1_innerframe.htm|title=Draft Eleventh Five Year Plan|publisher=Union Territory of Lakshadweep|accessdate=2012-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120511235551/http://lakshadweep.nic.in/FiveYearPlan_1_innerframe.htm|archive-date=2012-05-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==島嶼==
'''班加拉姆島'''為班加拉姆環礁中最大的島嶼，該島面積為2.3平方公里，島中央有座淡水池塘用於種植[[椰子|椰子]]與[[露兜樹屬|露兜樹屬]]植物。<ref>[http://www.mapsofindia.com/lakshadweep/tourism/bangaram-island.html Bangaram Islands] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110510124248/http://www.mapsofindia.com/lakshadweep/tourism/bangaram-island.html |date=2011-05-10 }}</ref>另一座大島為'''廷亞卡拉島'''，該島面積約略與班加拉姆島等同，其位於班加拉姆島東北方2.4公里處。此外，尚有三座小島：帕拉里一號、二好、三號島，其位於班加拉姆島東方。<ref name=gpo->{{cite web|url=http://permanent.access.gpo.gov/websites/pollux/pollux.nss.nima.mil/NAV_PUBS/SD/pub173/173sec05.pdf|title=Pub 173. Sailing Directions (Enroute): India & The Bay of Bengal|publisher=National Imagery and Mapping Agency|year=2002|accessdate=2012-05-07|archive-date=2017-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170201192202/https://permanent.access.gpo.gov/websites/pollux/pollux.nss.nima.mil/NAV_PUBS/SD/pub173/173sec05.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.orientalbirdclub.org/publications/forktail/10pdfs/Kurup-Lakshadweep.pdf |title=Birds of Lakshadweep Islands |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archive-date=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112215302/http://www.orientalbirdclub.org/publications/forktail/10pdfs/Kurup-Lakshadweep.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==旅遊==
班加拉姆島於1974年開放觀光客旅遊，但行事商業航班是有困難度的，因此觀光客多搭機自[[柯枝|柯枝]]至[[阿格蒂島|阿格蒂島]]之[[阿格蒂機場|阿格蒂機場]]再搭船趨之至此。<ref>[http://lakshadweeptourism.nic.in/ Tourism in Lakshadweep] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219123906/http://lakshadweeptourism.nic.in/ |date=2015-02-19 }}</ref>該島著名的觀光行程為多種探險活動<ref name=ib-ornithological>{{cite journal|url=http://www.indianbirds.in/pdfs/An%20ornithological%20expedition.pdf |title=An ornithological expedition to the Lakshadweep archipelago: Assessment of threats to pelagic and other birds and recommendations |author=Satish Pande, et al |journal=Indian Birds |volume=3 |issue=1 |accessdate=2012-05-07 |date=Jan–Feb 2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617052832/http://www.indianbirds.in/pdfs/An%20ornithological%20expedition.pdf |archivedate=2013-06-17 }}</ref>，包括[[水肺潛水|水肺潛水]]、[[浮潛|浮潛]]、魚類觀賞、珊瑚礁觀賞。<ref name=lakshadweep-bangaram>{{cite web|url=http://lakshadweep.nic.in/KL_Isl_Bangaram.htmL|title=Bangaram Island|publisher=Union Territory of Lakshadweep|accessdate=2012-05-07|archive-date=2013-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202093936/http://lakshadweep.nic.in/KL_Isl_bangaram.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

